    Protecting food and drink names from 1 January 2021
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">What food and drink producers with ‘geographical indication’ (GI) protection need to know from 1 January 2021.</p>

  </div>
